{"lemma":"عَنَزَة","slug":"عَنَزَة","root":"ع.ن.ز","root_slug":"ع-ن-ز","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ن-ز","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n30749","n30750"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8E%D9%86%D9%8E%D8%B2%D9%8E%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"goat","tags":["feminine","singulative"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Compare Hebrew עֵז (éz), Ugaritic 𐎓𐎇 (ʿz, “she-goat”), Akkadian 𒍚 (, enzu)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n30749","headword_ar":"عَنْزَةٌ","root":"Enz","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EanozN","text_ar":"عَنْزٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n30750","headword_ar":"عَنَزَةٌ","root":"Enz","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A short spear;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a small spear, between a staff and a spear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"longer than a staff and shorter than a spear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"said to be of the measure of half a spear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"somewhat more, having a head like that of the spear;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a staff shorter than a spear;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and, as some say,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zuj~","text_ar":"زُجّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. a"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pointed iron foot at the lower extremity"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (S, O, Msb, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like that of the spear:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the old man leans,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stays himself, upon it; and it is nearly like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Euk~aAzap","text_ar":"عُكَّازَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it is like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Euk~aAzap","text_ar":"عُكَّازَة"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which is a staff having a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zuj~","text_ar":"زُجّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Mgh:) pl. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EanazN","text_ar":"عَنَزٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", [or rather this is a coll. gen. n., of which"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EanazapN","text_ar":"عَنَزَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the n. un.,] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EanazaAtN","text_ar":"عَنَزَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) The Prophet is related to have prayed towards an"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eanazap","text_ar":"عَنَزَة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Mgh. [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sutorapN","text_ar":"سُتْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) ―         -b2-  Also The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Had~","text_ar":"حَدّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[by which may be meant either the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"edge"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"point"},{"kind":"text","text":"] of a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faA^os","text_ar":"فَاْس"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which means a hoe and an adz and an axe, and also a pickaxe]: (O, K:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"long"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Had~","text_ar":"حَدّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or iron"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"point"},{"kind":"text","text":"] of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miloTaAs","text_ar":"مِلْطَاس"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is a long double-headed pickaxe. (ISh, TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lTs","text_ar":"لطس"},{"kind":"text","text":".)       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain beast,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"found in the desert, slender in the muzzle, smaller than the dog, of the beasts of prey,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that seizes the camel in his rump,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and is seldom seen; asserted by the Arabs to be a devil:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O:) or, (K,) accord. to Aboo-Leyleh, (O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it is like the weasel"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in size:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it approaches the she-camel when she is lying down,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"then springs,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and enters into her vulva, and conceals itself therein,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"until it reaches the womb,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whereupon the she-camel"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dies on the spot"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"aborts and dies on the spot."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O.)"}],"source_refs":["O","K","S","TA","Msb","Mgh"]}]}}